## Technology Stack

### Frontend Technologies

- **HTML5/CSS3/JavaScript**: Core web technologies
- **Tailwind CSS**: Utility-first CSS framework for responsive design
- **Alpine.js** (optional): Lightweight JavaScript framework for interactivity
- **SVG**: For custom graphics and visualizations

### Backend & Data Services

- **Firebase**: Authentication, database, and hosting
  - Firebase Authentication
  - Firestore for database
  - Firebase Hosting (alternative to Vercel if needed)
- **IndexedDB**: Client-side database for offline functionality
- **LocalStorage/SessionStorage**: For user preferences and session data

### Mobile & Location Technologies

- **Progressive Web App (PWA)**: For installable web experiences
- **Capacitor**: To wrap web app as native app for app stores
- **Geolocation API**: Native browser API for location services
- **Mapbox/Leaflet.js**: Open source mapping solutions
- **OpenStreetMap**: Free geographic data

### Security & Authentication

- **Firebase Authentication**: For user management
- **JWT**: For secure token-based authentication
- **WebAuthn/FIDO2**: For biometric authentication support
- **Secure Storage**: For credential management
- **End-to-end encryption**: For sensitive data

### Development & Deployment Infrastructure

- **GitHub**: Version control and code repository
- **Vercel**: Deployment and hosting
- **Cloudflare**: DNS management and CDN
- **Jest**: JavaScript testing framework
- **Cypress** (optional): End-to-end testing

